# Calculator with TypeScript

![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/TypeScript-3178C6.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=TypeScript&logoColor=white)

The **Calculator with TypeScript** project was created for testing with TypeScript; it's a calculator that includes the operations addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, integer division, and the remainder of the division.
